bodyEn: These stylish and cosy felted wool slippers are soft, easy, natural and healthy.  Due to the properties of natural wool fiber they will let the skin on your feet breathe and will not let your feet get too hot or too cold.
bodyEt: Stiilsed ja mugavad vildist sussid on pehmed, kerged ja tervislikud. Naturaalse lambavilla temperatuuri hoidvate omaduste tõttu  lasevad vildist sussid nahal hingata - ei lase üle kuumeneda ega külmetuda.
